name: Gullhorn, Bjøllekua og Konni (Norvegian cow names)
description:
The cow girlfriends cards are illustrations from the children’s book "Kuvenninnene", written and illustrated by me. Why not send them to (cow)friends, and other friendly creatures. 

Printed on thick, high quality paper; Highland 300 g. Size 4.7 x 4.7 in / double cards / recycled envelopes / blank inside.
5 pack - all five designs in series included in one multi packet. Note: Five cards for the price of four.
